OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1776085869
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted carjacking in
OL,4,CSunderland
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for attempting
OL,7,Fto carry out a carjacking in
OL,8,FSunderland.
OL,10,FOn 17 March, Regan King approached a
OL,11,Fvehicle on Thompson Road in the
OL,12,FSouthwick area of the city and spoke
OL,13,Fto the driver, claiming to be homeless.
OL,15,FWhen the driver ignored him, King
OL,16,Fsuggested he had a weapon concealed in
OL,17,Fhis waistband and demanded the driver
OL,18,Fget out of the vehicle.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
