OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1776085869
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted carjacking in
OL,4,CSunderland
OL,6,FThe driver did get out and took the
OL,7,Fcar keys with them. King attempted to
OL,8,Fdrag the driver back to the vehicle
OL,9,Fbut two passers-by came to the
OL,10,Fdriver's aid and chased him away.
OL,12,FKing panicked and sought refuge at
OL,13,FSouthwick Police Station, but when
OL,14,Fofficers realised what had happened
OL,15,Fthey arrested him and he was later
OL,16,Fcharged with assault.
OL,18,FKing has been sentenced to 10 weeks in
OL,19,Fprison at South Tyneside Magistrates'
OL,20,FCourt.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
