OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1776085869
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted carjacking in
OL,4,CSunderland
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Julia Williams from
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police said: "We take
OL,8,Fpride in our stations being a place of
OL,9,Frefuge for those in need of help,
OL,10,Fhowever in this instance, it was
OL,11,Fstraight back to custody for King.
OL,13,F"Incidents of this nature are very
OL,14,Frare and are not something we take
OL,15,Flightly.
OL,17,F"Thanks to King's naivety, he ran
OL,18,Fstraight into the arms of the law, and
OL,19,Fwe were able to take swift and robust
OL,20,Faction against him."
